==Italian==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|VL.|it}} ''essere'', from {{etyl|la|it}} {{term|esse|lang=la}}, present active infinitive of {{term|sum|lang=la}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈɛs.se.re/|lang=it}}, {{X-SAMPA|/"Essere/|lang=it}}
* {{audio|It-essere.ogg|Audio}}
* {{hyphenation|ès|se|re}}

===Verb===
{{it-verb}}

# to [[be]]

